description:
Add _generate_hooks_json() function and generate hooks/hooks.json in plugin.

Implementation:
```python
def _generate_hooks_json() -> str:
    hooks_data = {
        "hooks": {
            "SessionStart": [{
                "matcher": "*",
                "hooks": [{
                    "type": "command",
                    "command": "echo '📋 Speculate workflows available. Type /speculate: to see commands.'"
                }]
            }]
        }
    }
    return json.dumps(hooks_data, indent=2) + "\n"
```

